<div class="row philosophy-bottom">
            <div class="poloroid-parent  pol-rotate-7-left">
                <div class="poloroid-img">
                    {% if section.settings.card_1_img != blank  %}
                        <img src="{{ 'bartley_v2.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="poloroid">
                    {% else %}
                        <img src="{{ block.settings.card_1_img | img_url: 'master' }}" alt="poloroid">
                    {% endif %}

                </div>
                <div class="poloroid-discription">
                    {% if section.settings.card_1_head != blank  %}
                        <h3>{{ section.settings.card_1_head }}</h3> 
                        {{ section.settings.card_1_desc }}
                    {% else %}
                        <h3>Bartley Weaver (@dreamweaveriv) Bodybuilder, Professional Eater, Tennessee Titan</h3> 
                        <p>I choose Real Good Foods because I can enjoy all of my favorite savory foods and still hit my macronutrient goals. Most of my savory cravings are loaded with carbs, but with the lineup at RGF I can tackle my cravings even on a low carb diet. I have used RGF throughout my contest preps the past three years. Dieting has never been easier! I love having flexibility to eat non-traditional bodybuilding food and still reach my physique goals.</p> 
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="poloroid-parent  pol-rotate-7-right">
                <div class="poloroid-img">
                    
                    {% if section.settings.card_2_img != blank  %}
                        <img src="{{ section.settings.card_2_img | img_url: 'master' }}" alt="poloroid">
                    {% else %}
                        <img src="{{ 'megan_v2.jpg' | asset_url }}" alt="poloroid">
                    {% endif %}

                </div>
                <div class="poloroid-discription">
                    {% if section.settings.card_2_head != blank  %}
                        <h3>{{ section.settings.card_2_head }}</h3> 
                        {{ section.settings.card_2_desc }}
                    {% else %}
                        <h3>Megan Cornelius (@pushupsnpumps) Type 1 Diabetic</h3> 
                        <p>I choose to eat Real Good Foods because they taste like many of my favorites, without having a huge impact on my blood sugar. Itâ€™s much easier to manage diabetes when you are able to find foods you love that are lower carb, but still taste great!</p> 
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
</div>

